  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Resolution to reduce gas prices",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mudita Peiris, chairman of Litro, has said that it has decided to reduce the price of gas.",
        "He said that he has decided to reduce the price of gas according to the price of gas in the world market."
      ],
      "title_ents": [],
